Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.16,0:48:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm conscious that I'm conscious.\NThat's all you're you're conscious that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.72,0:48:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you're conscious. That's all you're\Nconscious of. What is your name? Uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.44,0:49:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the date? Uh, uh, where you going\Ntoday? I don't know. That all comes
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.11,0:49:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,later. Don't you know? You have to have\Ncoffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.68,0:49:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The first awareness is that you are.\NSo
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.68,0:49:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the ultimate then the infinite context\Nthen is existence itself
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.28,0:49:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to be aware of existence. That which I\Nam is that out of which existence
