Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.76,0:49:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the content.\NOtherwise, you'd be different because
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.07,0:49:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you had a haircut today. You know, you\Ncan't be the content.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.88,0:49:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The sense of self, the identification of\Nwho am I with meditation and
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.72,0:49:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,contemplation, we'll talk more about it\Nas you know is how the techniques work
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.52,0:49:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,progressively.\NYou no longer say this is I. You no
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.59,0:49:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,longer say this is I. You no longer say\Nthis is I. The sense of I
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.20,0:50:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,withdraws\Nto become progressively the field
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.28,0:50:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,itself.\NProgressively one realizes
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.64,0:50:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that that which I am is the capacity for\Nconsciousness. I'm not even
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.28,0:50:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness.\NThe infinite capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.35,0:50:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to be conscious. I am prior to\Nconsciousness itself. That which I am is
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.11,0:50:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,before consciousness. Consciousness is\Nwilly willy crap stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.76,0:50:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,late in the game. Small fry like a\Nmouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.88,0:50:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you are is\Nbeyond consciousness. It's because of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.72,0:50:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what you are. Consciousness can spring\Nforth as an awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.55,0:50:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,as a vitional awareness.\Nthe sense of self.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.59,0:51:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Realize that you are beyond\Nconsciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.31,0:51:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for what you are,\Nconsciousness couldn't field itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.20,0:51:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel couldn't field itself into what you\Nit has to have existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.55,0:51:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So\Ndon't sell yourself short.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.72,0:51:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the infinite potentiality out of\Nwhich consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.96,0:51:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,arises out of which all the rest of this\NBS it passes itself off as you due to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.20,0:51:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the illusion of the ego because the ego\Nis narcissistic
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.55,0:51:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's in love with itself.\NYou see the ego for what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.55,0:51:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It thinks you're wonderful.\NYour thoughts are wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.72,0:51:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they aren't wonderful thoughts,\Nthey're important thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.59,0:52:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz your catastrophes are mindboggling.\NThis exaggeratedness
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.55,0:52:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is the magnification that the ego\Ncreates out of narcissism.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.40,0:52:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So what holds the whole ego together\Nthen is the that one is enamored of
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.24,0:52:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,oneself.\NEnamored.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.20,0:52:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego then takes credit for being who\Nyou are.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.40,0:52:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It also takes credit that it's the\Nauthor of your
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.92,0:52:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,existence.\NIt succeeds most of the time.
