Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.40,0:53:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,time.\NBig time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.52,0:53:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What I think in my what I feel is more\Nimportant than all of humanity. Can you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.04,0:53:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,believe the ego can be that big?\NNarcissism can grandiosity and
