Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.76,0:53:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,not even imaginable\Nthat you could get up front in a in a
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.48,0:53:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,world court and and say that you know\Nwhat you want for your country is more
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.31,0:53:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,important than the lives of all the\Ncountrymen. Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.11,0:53:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a crime. This is a mental\Nillness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.88,0:53:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A mental illness. So the egotism of the\Nego is unlimited.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.55,0:53:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlimited to think I'm not, you know,\NGod isn't God. I'm God.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.16,0:53:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh\Nthe refusal to surrender the authority
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.20,0:54:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,for the source of one's own existence to\NGod is what gets you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.96,0:54:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. So meditation quickly or be\Nbefore long brings about a certain
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.55,0:54:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,degree of humility.\NYou realize that that I'm not the
