Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.40,0:54:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,progressively more diffuse more general\Nbecomes the light of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.11,0:54:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,itself\Neventually becomes
