Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.92,0:54:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite reality,\Nthe infinite reality
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.35,0:55:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is the infin infinite potentiality.\NThe power of God is infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.59,0:55:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because God is infinite context.\NOut of infinite context arises all power
