Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.40,0:55:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what\Nthat's our reality. That's what we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.72,0:55:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the potentiality to become conscious\Nbecause you can choose
