Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.24,0:55:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets you into trouble sometimes. You\Ndon't know where the hell the light
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.83,0:56:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,switch is. I don't know. She said,\N"Where is the light switch?" I don't
