Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.31,0:56:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh because in youth, you're focused on\Nthingness. You know, all the gadgets,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.79,0:56:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the electronic gadgets that crowd the\Nmarketplace now are made out made by
