Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.44,1:07:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,see, it has nothing to do with now.\NAll kinds of books about now. Lord, save
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.68,1:07:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,us from now. Thank you, sir.\NIf there's no then and no when and no
