Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.40,1:11:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you remember it again. And wham. Because\Nas long as one is identifying with form,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.92,1:11:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,then you're going to keep reincarnating.\NThere's no way beyond it. I can see
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.67,1:11:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that. As long as you think I am anything\Nspecific, that specificness will then
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.60,1:11:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,create a new specificness.\NOnce you realize you're the field of the
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.19,1:11:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,infinite potentiality, you're beyond it.\NYou think you want another lifetime? I
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.64,1:11:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,got news for you.\NWhen you get there, you're not going to
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.00,1:11:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,like it anywhere. You like this\Nlifetime. I look back at previous
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.96,1:11:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,lifetimes. I didn't like anyone. I'm\Nbetter than any other one.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.92,1:12:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,On a certain level, they were all\Nhorrid. On a certain level, they were
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.19,1:12:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,all exciting. On a certain level, they\Nwere all everything else.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.44,1:12:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I could do without it. Heck, you had\Nenough lifetimes. I mean, you can do
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.60,1:12:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,without them. You just don't have a yen\Nfor another lifetime, folks. Like,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.23,1:12:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you've gone and seen so many movies.\NI'm not interested in movies. I never
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.23,1:12:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,watched movies. I mean, I've seen them\Nall. I've seen every twist and turn and
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.36,1:12:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,writer's fantasy about how you can\Nphrase this, express that. I've seen
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.96,1:12:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,every actors and actresses\Ndoing it there and I just don't get it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.80,1:12:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,entertaining anymore.\NAll right. Enlightenment then would be
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.40,1:12:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the dissolution of the identification\Nwith content.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.15,1:12:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,with content,\Nwith existence as form,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.12,1:13:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,even with existence itself. That which I\Nam is beyond existence. Existence came
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.32,1:13:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,out of that which I am just as\Nconsciousness arose out of that which
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.60,1:13:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't be at the effect of anything.\NThere's nothing causing anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.80,1:13:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently,\Nanything phrased within the context of
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.67,1:13:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,causality cannot have any cannot be the\Nabsolute reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.80,1:13:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In as much as one lifetime does not\Nkarmmically cause the next lifetime. No,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.64,1:13:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,something outside of all of those\Nlifetimes
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.15,1:13:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to bring them into physical\Nmanifestation.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.48,1:13:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be the content of each\Nlifetime. You have to be the source out
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.00,1:13:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of which those lifetimes are arising and\None is re- choosing reincarnation.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.12,1:14:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Contemplation then is just walking about\Nand you see you can do it right now. You
