Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.88,1:14:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity to be aware of the\Nphenomena
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.84,1:14:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you are. You hold the capacity.\NWhat you are is the capacity to be aware
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.15,1:14:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of any of this. Now you can pay as much\Nattention to it as you want. You see
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.52,1:14:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that's valitional.\NYou can either pay attention to it. You
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.15,1:14:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,can identify with it or not. and I'm\Nfine with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.88,1:14:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even to say what day it is is a\Nmentation. It's no day right now at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.76,1:14:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no day that it is today any\Nmore than there is any month that it is
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.76,1:14:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,today or any year that it is today.\NThose are all madeups
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.80,1:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,just wordingnesses\Nconveniences
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.67,1:15:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world of form. That's very\Nconvenient to say. I'll see you
