Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.48,1:15:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very easy to get that you are\Nbeyond that which is in physicality.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.92,1:15:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite awareness is radiating\Nforth as
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.76,1:15:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the seeming phenomena.\NBut you get you're that you're beyond
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.40,1:15:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,all that.\NYou get that you're the field out of
