Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.60,1:16:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody agree?\NWe're all the infinite field out of
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.44,1:16:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,which consciousness arises.\NNot we're not the product of
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.84,1:16:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness.\NWe're its capacity, its source
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.15,1:16:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which consciousness arises.\NThe manifest arises out of the
