Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.60,1:17:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,creates the illusion of causality.\NThere are no cause out there at all,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.64,1:17:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,folks.\NWhen I was a kid, I lived out in the
